MAN, 82, CHARGED WITH MURDER OF WIFE<
By Sam Greenhill, PA News<
An 82-year-old man was appearing in court today charged with murdering his
wife after she was gunned down in their home.<
Essex Police said Leslie Parsons was accused of killing 87-year-old Dorothy
and was also charged with firearms offences.<
Mrs Parsons died on January 8 in a double shooting at the couple's home on
Golden Lane, Thorpe-le-Soken, near Clacton, Essex.<
Parsons is due to appear before Colchester magistrates.<
